<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>jǐ dù fēng yǔ 迦南329</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 jǐ dù fēng yǔ yǔ zhōng yě jiàn qíng tiān,
 qí qū zhǎng lù lù shàng cháng yǒu ēn diǎn,
 yī shēng diān pèi liú lí, xiào róng mǎn miàn,
 qīng qīng kǔ kǔ, gēn zhe zhǔ yī nián yòu yī nián.
 shéi néng liǎng xiù qīng fēng yī chén bù rǎn
 xiōng dì bǐ cǐ xiāng ài rú dà wèi hé yuē ná dān.
 zhǔ ài rú mián mián xì yǔ zī rùn gàn kě xīn tián
 bù qī dài míng tiān duō měi hǎo zhǐ qiú tiān tiān jiàn zhǔ miàn.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>329</hymn_number>
</song>